  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Also, one thing we are not doing good in IS V1 is that we do have movies that have five stars, but we are unable to refine only on them.\n\nI would add this: if the Algolia stats reveals that there are some objects reaching the maximum rating, then show the refinement for ★★★★★ because it's useful for users.\n\nAnd we can go even further, by denoting the available/unavailable ranges like how it's done today:\n\n![2016-09-21-154338_244x136_scrot](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/123822/18713342/3c4a400a-8012-11e6-9d87-b362179cf1ae.png)\n",
