  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "> However if the count for a line is 0, I currently didn't add a specific classname for it. Do you want this to be added ?\n\nI would say yes, since the current starRating widget has this ability (see https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/pull/1317#issuecomment-248616488), and it is very valuable. If the range is not relevant then we should hint the display/user. (Like a disabled state, or something consistent with Pagination for example)\n\nWhat do you think?\n",
